There is no single license for this entire workspace.

This workspace contains multiple layers with different intended visibility:

- OPEN / free developer tools: license must be chosen per package before publication.
- COMMERCIAL apps and bundles: proprietary unless an explicit product license says otherwise.
- BOOKS / CANON / EDITORIAL: all rights reserved unless specific samples are approved.
- PRIVATE GAME / TCG: proprietary, private, not open source.
- VENDOR / THIRD-PARTY code: remains under its upstream license and must not be relicensed here.

Do not publish this workspace as a whole under this file.
